+ Directions to Disneyland from phoenix
+
+ Take I-10 west across the AZ/CA State line 
+ Continue west on the I-10 through Palm Springs 
+ Take the exit onto CA Route 60 westbound towards Riverside 
+ Merge onto the I-215 northbound 
+ Go 3.5 miles to the interchange with CA Route 91
+ Take CA Route 91 west towards Corona
+ Continue west to CA Route 57 
+ Take CA Route 57 south towards Santa Ana
+ Take the exit for Katella Avenue westbound 
+ Go north for 2 miles until you see the Hollywood Tower Of Terror
+
+ You have arrived!

